        "description": "\u003cp\u003eMAKS 4080 MICROORGANISM CONTROL AGENT\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGENERAL DESCRIPTION\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMAKS 4080\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026nbsp;is a combination of heterocyclic compounds formulated in an aqueous solution.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePRINCIPAL USES\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMAKS 4080\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026nbsp;is a broad spectrum, non-oxidizing micro microorganism control agent for industrial open re-circulating, cooling systems, air washers, brewery pasteurizers and closed systems. It is designed to provide excellent control of microbiological growth, algea and associated deposits.\u0026nbsp;\u003cstrong\u003eMAKS 4080\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026nbsp;is particularly well suited for use in systems with high levels of process contamination, as in the fertilizer, refinery, and chemical, industries.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePRODUCT BENEFITS\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\t\u003cli\u003eEffective against a broad spectrum of microorganisms over extended periods\u003c/li\u003e\t\u003cli\u003eHelps to minimize slime problems which can cause costly reductions in heat transfer\u003c/li\u003e\t\u003cli\u003eMinimum discharge problems; active molecules are environmentally degradable\u003c/li\u003e\t\u003cli\u003eEasy to apply; active at low dosages.\u003c/li\u003e\t\u003cli\u003eOrganic based and can provide minimum 90% protection\u003c/li\u003e\t\u003cli\u003eDoes not cause precipitation; does not act with other additives\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e",
