        "brand": "TopJet",
        "category": "Industrial Equipment",
        "description": "\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe KT Series macro character inkjet printing systems encode any type of packaging or moving object through alphanumeric messages. These systems can use a 7-dot (KT7) or 16-dot (KT16) printhead with nominal character heights from 12 mm up to 75 mm.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThey can be easily integrated into any type of production line or plant to print text, batches, time and date. Absorbent board, wood, coated paper, glass, metals, plastics, polystyrene, ceramics, bricks, natural stones, among others.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
